special_powers.name: LIGHTNING FIELD
special_powers.description: Black Lightning can use Energy Shield/Deflection and Poison. When Black Lightning is hit by a close combat attack and actions resolve, deal the attacker 1 damage.

special_powers.name: CAN'T BE TRUSTED
special_powers.description: Adjacent opposing characters can't use team abilities.

special_powers.name: BOUNCING AROUND THE WORLD AT LIGHT SPEED
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, you may roll a d6. If you do, replace Doctor Light's speed value with the result plus his printed speed value until your next turn.

special_powers.name: REFORMING MYSELF
special_powers.description: Doctor Light can use Energy Shield/Deflection. If he has been given a move action this turn, he can use Regeneration as a free action.

special_powers.name: WHITTLE DOWN THE STRONGEST FOE
special_powers.description: When Katana targets an opposing character with the highest point value on its force with an attack, modify her attack and damage values by +1.

special_powers.name: MY HUSBAND'S KISS
special_powers.description: Katana can use Precision Strike and Steal Energy.

special_powers.name: VIBRATION
special_powers.description: Vibe can use Quake.

special_powers.name: INTERRUPT VIBRATIONAL ANOMALIES
special_powers.description: Opposing characters within range must be given a double power action instead of a power or move action to activate Charge Hypersonic Speed, Phasing/Teleport, or Running Shot.

special_powers.name: THE DOMAIN OF ATLANTIS
special_powers.description: When Atlantean occupies water terrain, modify his combat values by +1.

special_powers.name: CANNIBAL RACE
special_powers.description: When an adjacent friendly character with "dolphin symbol" or "transporter dolphin symbol" is KO'd, you may heal The Trench of 2 damage.

special_powers.name: UNDERSEA PREDATORS
special_powers.description: The Trench can use Charge. If it began its turn occupying water terrain, it can use Hypersonic Speed.

special_powers.name: SAFETY IN NUMBERS
special_powers.description: When D.E.O. Agent is adjacent to a friendly character with the Police keyword or team ability, both characters can use Stealth.

special_powers.name: LOCKDOWN
special_powers.description: Give Blackgate Guard a free action and choose an opposing character within range and line of fire. Until your next turn, that character can't automatically break away and modifies its break away rolls by -2.

special_powers.name: JAILBREAK
special_powers.description: Give a Blackgate Inmate a power action and choose a friendly character within 4 squares and line of fire; that character can use Sidestep this turn.

special_powers.name: MINION: SHOCK TROOPS OF APOKOLIPS
special_powers.description: When a friendly character with the Apokolips keyword and a higher point value is within 8 squares, Parademon can use the Colossal Stamina ability.

special_powers.name: TWISTED COUPLE
special_powers.description: When a friendly character named Johnny Quick is adjacent to Atomica, they both modify their attack values by +1 if not already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: HIDDEN LOYALTIES
special_powers.description: Atomica can use Shape Change. When she does and the attacker has a shared keyword, modify her Shape Change result by +2.

special_powers.name: TRAVEL TO PRIME EARTH
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your first turn you may place up to 6 water terrain markers in any squares at least 5 squares from any player's starting area. These markers remain until the end of the game.

special_powers.name: VENOMOUS BITE
special_powers.description: Copperhead can use Flurry and Incapacitate. When he uses Flurry and hits the same character with both attacks, give that character an action token.

special_powers.name: SYMBOLS AND SIGNS CONTROL OUR LIVES
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, choose a combat symbol other than "boot symbol", "fist symbol", "shield symbol", or "starburst symbol". When an opposing character with the chosen symbol is targeted by Mind Control, modify that character's defense value by -1 or, if Signalman is the attacker, by -2.

special_powers.name: SUBJECT B-ZERO
special_powers.description: Bizarro can use Super Strength.  Adjacent friendly characters named Lex Luthor can use Mastermind but only to transfer damage to Bizarro, regardless of point value.

special_powers.name: TRIDENT OF NEPTUNE, RELIC OF ATLANTIS
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, choose one to last until you chose again: Aquaman can use Enhancement and Leadership or, Aquaman can use Energy Explosion or, Aquaman can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast.

special_powers.name: SUBTLE TELEPATHIC PUSH
special_powers.description: Once per turn, Aquaman can use either Outwit or Perplex. When he does, he may target characters with the "dolphin" or "transporter dolphin" symbol anywhere on the map.

special_powers.name: HYDRAULICS ARE GO!
special_powers.description: Cyborg can use Running Shot and Improved Movement: Elevated, Hindering.

special_powers.name: WHITE NOISE
special_powers.description: Cyborg can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast.  When he does, give an action token to hit characters with no action tokens.

special_powers.name: CH2=C(CH3)CH=CH2
special_powers.description: When Firestorm would take damage from another character assigned a resource, Firestorm ignores that damage and rolls a d6. When he does, on a result of 1-3, deal firestorm 1 unavoidable damage. This ability can't be ignored.

special_powers.name: HYDROGEN? THAT ONE'S EASY
special_powers.description: Firestorm can use Energy Explosion and Precision Strike.

special_powers.name: WATCH AND LEARN
special_powers.description: Adjacent friendly characters with the Justice League of America keyword can use the Sharpshooter ability.

special_powers.name: ONE-IN-A-MILLION SHOT
special_powers.description: Once per game, give Green Arrow a power action. At the beginning of your next turn he can use Ranged Combat Expert as a free action to target any character occupying outdoor terrain on the map.

special_powers.name: SHARP EYES AND SHARP ARROWS
special_powers.description: Green Arrow can use Enhancement and Ranged Combat Expert.

special_powers.name: INSPIRATIONAL ALLY
special_powers.description: When a second action token would be given to an adjacent friendly character, roll a d6.  If that character has the Justice League of America keyword, add 2 to the result.  If the result is 6 or higher, that character can use Willpower this turn.

special_powers.name: IT'S IN THE CARDS
special_powers.description: When an opposing character targets Madame Xanadu or an adjacent friendly character with the Justice League Dark keyword with an attack, you may choose a number between 1 and 6. After actions resolve, those characters heal one click for each die in the final attack roll showing the chosen number.

special_powers.name: RISE OF THE VAMPIRES AND BEYOND
special_powers.description: If I, Vampire is 75 points, he is KO'd if he crosses the red KO line.  If I, Vampire is 170 points, he isn't KO'd when he crosses the red KO line.

special_powers.name: ULTIMATE VAMPIRE
special_powers.description: I, Vampire can use Hypersonic Speed, the Mystics team ability, and his powers can't be countered.

special_powers.name: EMPOWERED BY CAIN'S DEMISE
special_powers.description: When turning the dial, if this click is revealed due to damage taken from an opposing character's attack, stop turning the dial.  This power can't be ignored.

special_powers.name: RESURRECTION ENERGIES
special_powers.description: I, Vampire can use Probability Control.  Give him a power action and heal each adjacent friendly character of 1 damage.

special_powers.name: HIDING FROM THE SUN
special_powers.description: When Ultraman occupies hindering terrain, his powers and abilities can't be countered.

special_powers.name: TRAINING AND TECHNIQUE
special_powers.description: Owlman can use Combat Reflexes, Toughness, and Willpower.

special_powers.name: SMARTER THAN YOU KNOW
special_powers.description: Owlman can use Outwit. Opposing characters within 6 squares can't use Outwit to target a character with a higher point value than themselves.

special_powers.name: YOU'LL BETRAY EACH OTHER
special_powers.description: Opposing characters within 6 squares that are adjacent to and share a keyword with each other modify their defense values by -1 unless already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: YOU'LL BETRAY EACH OTHER
special_powers.description: Opposing characters within 6 squares that are adjacent to and share a keyword with each other modify their defense values by -1 unless already modified by this effect.

special_powers.name: AQUATIC EXTENSION
special_powers.description: Mera's range value is equal to 1 plus the number of squares of water terrain she occupies or is adjacent to.

special_powers.name: A DAY WITHOUT WATER
special_powers.description: When an opposing character within 3 squares is given a non-free action, after actions resolve, place a Thirst token on that character's card. Characters with any Thirst tokens on their card modify their combat values by -1. When a character clears action tokens, remove one Thirst token from its card.

special_powers.name: TIDAL WAVE
special_powers.description: Once per game, give Ocean Master a double power action and choose an edge of the map your starting area is adjacent to. Roll 2d6 and double the result. Any squares within a number of squares away from the chosen edge are water terrain in addition to any other types this game.

special_powers.name: ELECTROCUTE
special_powers.description: Ocean Master can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast. When he does, Ocean Master may target any number of opposing characters within range that are occupying water terrain.

special_powers.name: FEAR RULES YOU NOW
special_powers.description: Scarecrow can use Incapacitate, Mind Control, and Poison. When he uses Incapacitate to place a second action token on a character, modify its attack value by -1 until your next turn, and after actions resolve he can use Mind Control as a free action targeting each of those characters.

special_powers.name: A DIFFERENT KIND OF BUTLER
special_powers.description: When a friendly character uses Probability Control and an action token would be assigned as a result, you may deal The Outsider 1 unavoidable damage instead.

special_powers.name: DIMENSIONAL PORTAL
special_powers.description: Give The Outsider a power action and place up to 2 friendly characters that share a keyword with The Outsider into squares adjacent to him, then use Smoke Cloud as a free action. Characters placed this way can't be given non-free actions until your next turn.

special_powers.name: SINKHOLE
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, you may choose to lower all elevated terrain by 1 elevation level, to a minimum of 1. The Outsider can use Quake, and can use it as a free action if he has 2 action tokens.

special_powers.name: INDIAN EMPIRE OF CRIME
special_powers.description: The Outsider ignores opposing characters' Shape Change. When he deals damage, that damage can't be transferred. Non-adjacent characters can't target The Outsider with Outwit.

special_powers.name: I'M NOT ONE OF YOU AND I DON'T BELONG HERE
special_powers.description: When he is adjacent to an opposing character, The Outsider can use Sidestep, and automatically breaks away when doing so.

special_powers.name: MAGIC AVOIDANCE
special_powers.description: Friendly characters with the Secret Society of Super Villains keyword ignore the Mystics team ability.

special_powers.name: EYE SEE YOUR MAGIC
special_powers.description: Dr. Sivana can use Outwit. Dr. Sivana may activate Outwit with a power action and when he does, the countered power or ability is also countered on all opposing characters within 8 squares of Dr. Sivana that share a keyword with the target.

special_powers.name: RIGHT UNDER THEIR NOSES
special_powers.description: Lex Luthor begins the game with a Subterfuge token on his card. When Lex Luthor has a Subterfuge token on his card, opposing characters can only target him if they began the turn adjacent to him. When Lex Luthor targets an opposing character with an attack, remove all Subterfuge tokens from his card.

special_powers.name: BACK UNDERGROUND
special_powers.description: When this click is revealed, add a Subterfuge token to Lex Luthor's card.

special_powers.name: THE SYNDICATE IS BAD FOR BUSINESS
special_powers.description: Lex Luthor can use Leadership and Outwit. When he uses Leadership and succeeds, he may instead remove the action token from a friendly character with the Injustice League keyword within 3 squares and regardless of point value.

special_powers.name: ELEMENTAL ARTISTE
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, choose one: Earth, Fire, or Ice. Element Woman can use the associated powers until your next turn. Earth: Barrier and Impervious. Fire: Energy Explosion and Penetrating/Psychic Blast. Ice: Incapacitate and Perplex.

special_powers.name: CONNECTION TO THE RED
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, give Vixen a free action and choose one of "boot symbol", "wing symbol", or "dolphin symbol", and one of "tiny symbol", "starburst symbol", "giant symbol". Vixen has the chosen symbols until you choose again.

special_powers.name: ANIMAL SPIRITS
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, give Vixen a free action and choose: Blades/Claws/Fangs, Close Combat Expert, Flurry, Poison or Sidestep. Vixen can use the chosen power until you choose again. If Vixen is part of a Justice League of America themed team, she may choose 2 powers instead.

special_powers.name: WILLPOWER THROUGH MY GUN
special_powers.description: Green Lantern can use Improved Targeting: Hindering, Opposing Characters, Adjacent.

special_powers.name: PROTECTING MY NEW FRIENDS
special_powers.description: Green Lantern can use Barrier and Combat Reflexes. When he uses Barrier, he may place one additional blocking terrain marker adjacent to each friendly character within range and with the Justice League of America keyword. These additional markers don't need to be adjacent to other markers.

special_powers.name: PURE OF HEART
special_powers.description: Shazam! can use Defend.

special_powers.name: SHAZAM!
special_powers.description: Shazam! can use Flurry, Sidestep, and the Quintessence team ability.

special_powers.name: A GIFT FROM THE WIZARD FOR MY FRIENDS
special_powers.description: Give Shazam! a free action, choose any adjacent friendly characters and deal him 1 unavoidable damage. Modify the combat values of chosen characters by +1 until your next turn, even if this power is lost.

special_powers.name: CALL THE LIGHTNING
special_powers.description: Freddy Freeman can use Pulse Wave as if he has a range value of 9. When he does and actions resolve, heal Freddy Freeman of 1 damage for each hit opposing character.

special_powers.name: I OWN THE SKY
special_powers.description: Hawkman can use Charge and doesn't halve his speed value when using it. When he does and hits, he can use Sidestep this turn.

special_powers.name: NO MATTER THE ODDS, THEY WILL FALL BEFORE ME
special_powers.description: Hawkman can use Quake. If Hawkman is part of a Justice League of America themed team, give him a move action and after it resolves, he can use Quake as a free action.

special_powers.name: POSSESS THE LOCALS
special_powers.description: When a countdown click appears, stop clicking the dial, place a Spirit marker in Deadman's square, and place him on this card. At the beginning of your turn, if Deadman is on this card, click his dial once clockwise. When you do and a countdown click is no longer present, place him within 4 squares of the Spirit marker, remove that marker, and Deadman can't be given a non-free action this turn. If Deadman is on his card and no friendly characters are on the map, he is KO'd.

special_powers.name: WHOSE BODY AM I IN?
special_powers.description: Deadman can use Phasing/Teleport and Shape Change. When an adjacent friendly character with the Justice League Dark keyword makes an attack, opposing characters can't use Shape Change.

special_powers.name: THIS GUY HAS A GUN!
special_powers.description: Deadman has a range value of 6 and can use the Sharpshooter ability. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: NECRONAUTS
special_powers.description: When Frankenstein or a friendly character KO an opposing character with a point value of 50 or more with an attack, all friendly characters with the Justice League Dark keyword can be given a move action as a free action this turn.

special_powers.name: ARCHANGEL'S SWORD
special_powers.description: Frankenstein can use Blades/Claws/Fangs. When he does and the result is a 4-6, hit characters can't be healed this game, even if this power is lost.

special_powers.name: ABSORB YOUR ENERGIES
special_powers.description: Deathstorm can use Energy Shield/Deflection and Toughness. If this click is revealed as a result of taking damage from a ranged combat attack, after actions resolve, roll a d6 and heal him of damage equal to the result.

special_powers.name: HUMAN EXPERIMENTATION
special_powers.description: Deathstorm can use Perplex. When he does, if he targets a character 75 points or less, he may modify a combat value other than damage by +2 or -2.

special_powers.name: JUSTICE LEAGUE DATA HOARD
special_powers.description: Opposing characters with the Justice League or Justice League of America keyword can't use Outwit, Perplex, or Probability Control to target The Grid or adjacent characters friendly to him.

special_powers.name: HAVE A NICE DAY!
special_powers.description: Opposing characters within 6 squares can't ignore pushing damage.

special_powers.name: TAKING OVER CYBORG'S FRAME
special_powers.description: The Grid can use Outwit and Shape Change. When a character with a power countered by The Grid targets him with an attack, his Shape Change succeeds on a result of 3-6.

special_powers.name: SPEED FORCE
special_powers.description: When Johnny Quick moves at least one square and hits one or more adjacent characters, you may place a Speed token on this card after actions resolve. Increase Johnny Quick's speed value by the number of Speed tokens on this card.

special_powers.name: A DIFFERENT CONNECTION TO SPEED
special_powers.description: Give Johnny Quick a free action, remove a Speed token and he can use Perplex until your next turn, but may only use it to target an opposing character. That character can't use speed powers until your next turn.

special_powers.name: WHAT A RUSH!
special_powers.description: Give Johnny Quick a free action when he has no action tokens and choose 1 or 2. Increase his combat values by the amount chosen until your next turn and at the end of your turn, deal him unavoidable damage equal to the amount chosen.

special_powers.name: THE RING IS KILLING ME
special_powers.description: When Power Ring is given a non-free action other than a move action, after actions resolve roll a d6. On a result of 1-2, deal him 1 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: WE'RE GOING SOMEWHERE?
special_powers.description: Power Ring can use Phasing/Teleport. When Power Ring uses the Carry ability, he may carry up to 3 friendly characters that share a keyword with him regardless of their speed symbols.

special_powers.name: POWER OF VOLTHOOM'S RING
special_powers.description: Power Ring can use Perplex. Opposing characters within 6 squares can't use Perplex to target characters with a point value higher than their own.

special_powers.name: FEASTING ON YOUR FIRE
special_powers.description: Killer Frost can use Steal Energy. She can use it normally or during ranged combat attacks that target a single character. Opposing characters using Steal Energy do not heal when a friendly character with the Secret Society of Super Villians keyword adjacent to Killer Frost takes damage from their attack.

special_powers.name: ICE BARRICADE
special_powers.description: Killer Frost can use Barrier and Energy Shield/Deflection.

special_powers.name: COLD SNAP
special_powers.description: When Killer Frost is hit by an attack and actions resolve, give the attacker an action token, if you can't, deal the attacker 1 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: DEMON HUNTER
special_powers.description: Adjacent friendly characters and friendly characters with the Justice League Dark keyword ignore the Mystics team ability.

special_powers.name: SUPERNATURAL EXORCISM
special_powers.description: When Blue Devil damages a character and a special power is revealed that stops that dial from turning, after actions resolve, deal that character 2 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: HELLFIRE
special_powers.description: Blue Devil can use Energy Explosion and Penetrating/Psychic Blast.

special_powers.name: REGENERATE FROM ANY WOUND
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, you may heal Shaggy Man of 1 damage.

special_powers.name: RESTORE LOST LIMBS
special_powers.description: Shaggy Man can use Regeneration.  When he does, don't subtract 2 from the result.

special_powers.name: SEEMINGLY IMMORTAL
special_powers.description: After clearing tokens at the end of your turn, if Vandal Savage has two action tokens, heal him of 1 damage.

special_powers.name: I WAS ALEXANDER, GENGHIS, VLAD...
special_powers.description: Vandal Savage can use Leadership. When he does and succeeds, modify the attack value of all friendly characters by +1 until your next turn.

special_powers.name: TRAINED IN EVERY STYLE OF FIGHTING
special_powers.description: Vandal Savage can use Close Combat Expert. When he does, he can use Probability Control during that action.

special_powers.name: TACTICIAN THAT WON A THOUSAND WARS
special_powers.description: Vandal Savage can use Outwit and Perplex as if he has a range value of 8 and Improved Targeting: Characters.

special_powers.name: DEATH TO THE GUARDIANS
special_powers.description: Sinestro can use Pulse Wave. Opposing characters that can use the Quintessence team ability instead can't use it and modify their combat values by -1.

special_powers.name: FEAR THE SINESTRO CORP
special_powers.description: Sinestro can use Perplex, but only to decrease combat values. Until your next turn, a character targeted by this Perplex can't target Sinestro unless the targeted character or Sinestro are the only characters on their force on the map.

special_powers.name: A NEW KIND OF JUSTICE LEAGUE
special_powers.description: Adjacent friendly characters with a lower point value and the Justice League keyword can use the Superman Ally team ability. Friendly characters named Batman or Wonder Woman don't have to be adjacent or a lower point value.

special_powers.name: FREEZE BREATH
special_powers.description: Superman can use Incapacitate. When he does, if he uses it as a close combat action, he may target all adjacent opposing characters. If he uses it as a ranged combat action and hits the target, an area of effect may include all untargeted characters that are adjacent to a hit target.

special_powers.name: TRUE INVULNERABILITY COMES FROM WITHIN
special_powers.description: Superman can use Impervious. At the beginning of your turn, if Superman was damaged by an opposing character's attack since your last turn, heal him of 1 damage.

special_powers.name: INSPIRING HERO
special_powers.description: Superman can use Leadership. When he does and succeeds, modify the attack and defense values of all friendly characters by +1 until your next turn.

special_powers.name: A NEW KIND OF JUSTICE LEAGUE
special_powers.description: Adjacent friendly characters with a lower point value and the Justice League keyword can use the Batman Ally team ability. Friendly characters named Superman or Wonder Woman don't have to be adjacent or a lower point value.

special_powers.name: UTILITY BELT
special_powers.description: Give Batman a free action and choose a standard attack or damage power. Batman can use that power until your next turn.

special_powers.name: WORLD'S GREATEST DETECTIVE AND STRATEGIST
special_powers.description: Batman can use Outwit and Perplex. When he has no action tokens, he can use Probability Control.

special_powers.name: A NEW KIND OF JUSTICE LEAGUE
special_powers.description: Adjacent friendly characters with a lower point value and the Justice League keyword can use Support. Friendly characters named Batman or Superman don't have to be adjacent or a lower point value.

special_powers.name: LASSO OF TRUTH
special_powers.description: Adjacent opposing characters that have been hit by Wonder Woman since the beginning of your last turn can't use Outwit, Perplex, or Probability Control.

special_powers.name: STRONGEST WOMAN IN THE WORLD
special_powers.description: Wonder Woman can use Super Strength. If Wonder Woman isn't holding an object and is adjacent to a square of blocking terrain, you may give her a free action to destroy that square of blocking terrain. If you do, place a standard heavy object into that square.

special_powers.name: DEFLECTED BULLETS
special_powers.description: When Wonder Woman is targeted by a ranged combat attack that misses, after actions resolve give the attacker an action token. If you can't, deal the attacker 1 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: WE OPERATE FROM THE SHADOWS, ALRIGHT?
special_powers.description: John Constantine can use Stealth. Adjacent friendly characters with the Justice League Dark keyword can use Stealth.

special_powers.name: ULTIMATE CON MAN
special_powers.description: Once per turn, choose Outwit or Perplex and John Constantine can use that power until your next turn. When he uses the chosen power to target an opposing character, that character can't use the chosen power until your next turn. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: I MAKE MY OWN LUCK
special_powers.description: John Constantine can use Probability Control, but can use it twice each turn.

special_powers.name: I THOUGHT WE WERE FRIENDS
special_powers.description: Nick Necro can use Stealth. At the beginning of the game, you may choose an opposing character and that character can't target Nick Necro unless Nick Necro or that character is the only character on its force on the map.

special_powers.name: MYSTICAL ARTIFACTS ARE DRAWN TO ME
special_powers.description: When this click is revealed due to damage taken from an opposing character's attack, if the attacking character has a relic or resource attachment assigned to them, stop turning the dial. That opponent chooses one: deal the attacker 3 unavoidable damage; or heal Nick Necro of 1 damage and remove from the game up to one relic or resource attachment assigned to the attacker.

special_powers.name: TAUGHT YOU EVERYTHING YOU KNOW
special_powers.description: Nick Necro can use Outwit. Give Nick Necro a power action and target a character within range and line of fire. That character can't use combat or team abilities and its combat values can't be greater than its printed values until your next turn.

special_powers.name: MARTIAN TELEPATHY
special_powers.description: Opposing forces subtract one from their action total if not already reduced by any other effect.

special_powers.name: THERE ARE MANY WAYS TO HIDE IN PLAIN SIGHT
special_powers.description: Martian Manhunter can use Phasing/Teleport, Shape Change, and Stealth.

special_powers.name: EXPELLED UNNATURAL MAGIC
special_powers.description: Tim Hunter and adjacent friendly characters with the Justice League Dark keyword can't be the target of opposing characters' Probability Control.

special_powers.name: DESTINED TO BE THE WORLD'S GREATEST MAGICIAN
special_powers.description: Tim Hunter can use Energy Shield/Deflection, Probability Control, Pulse Wave, Super Senses, and Willpower.

special_powers.name: EVERYONE'S ANNOYINGLY CONCERNED FOR MY WELFARE
special_powers.description: Before any attack roll, Tim Hunter may replace his defense value with the unmodified defense value of any adjacent friendly character with the Mystical keyword.

special_powers.name: MENTORED BY THE TRENCHCOAT BRIGADE
special_powers.description: Give Tim Hunter a free action and choose an adjacent friendly character with the Mystical keyword and one or more action tokens.  Tim Hunter can use the powers possessed by the chosen character until the beginning of your next turn.

special_powers.name: ANANYM
special_powers.description: When you place your characters at the start of the game, you may turn Zantanna to click 6. If you do, this game turn her dial counter-clockwise when she is damaged and clockwise when she is healed and she can't heal past click 6. This trait can't be ignored.

special_powers.name: GNIGNITS SKCIGAM
special_powers.description: Zatanna can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast and Precision Strike.

special_powers.name: PLEH MEHT
special_powers.description: Give Zatanna a free action and choose one of the following to last until your next turn: Zatanna can use Barrier and Perplex or Zatanna can use Enhancement and Probability Control.

special_powers.name: PANDORA'S BOX
special_powers.description: When building your force, JLTW #R101 Pandora's Box costs 12 points less.

special_powers.name: PREPARE THE WAY
special_powers.description: Give The Outsider a power action and place him and a friendly character in each other's squares. Unless that friendly character shares a keyword with The Outsider, it couldn't have been given any actions this turn and also can't be give any actions this turn.

special_powers.name: HIDDEN IN OUR MIDST
special_powers.description: The Outsider can use Mastermind. When he does, friendly characters within 6 squares that are not within ay opposing character's line of fire are considered adjacent and a lower point value.

special_powers.name: YOU WILL PAY
special_powers.description: If Black Adam is the only character on your force that has not been KO'd, modify his attack value by +1. If Black Adam is the only character on your force that has not been KO'd and your force is a named themed team, instead modify all of Black Adam's combat values by +1.

special_powers.name: BY MAGIC EMPOWERED
special_powers.description: Black Adam can use Super Strength. Black Adam can't be targeted by Outwit unless the targeting character has the Mystical keyword.

special_powers.name: JUSTICE WITHOUT MERCY
special_powers.description: Black Adam can use Charge and Flurry. When Black Adam uses Charge he doesn't halve his speed value and, if he isn't carrying a character or holding an object, he can use Improved Movement: Destroy Blocking.

special_powers.name: THE THUNDER OF THE GODS
special_powers.description: Black Adam can use Quake but his damage value becomes his printed damage value instead of 2.

special_powers.name: PSYCHIC JUGGERNAUT
special_powers.description: Despero can't be the target of Incapacitate, Mind Control, Outwit, or Penetrating/Psychic Blast by characters of a lower point value.

special_powers.name: PSYCHIC TRANSFERENCE
special_powers.description: Despero can use Steal Energy, and can use it normally or during ranged combat attacks that target a single character. When he does, increase the amount healed by 1 for each of the following the target can use: Incapacitate, Mind Control, Outwit, or Penetrating/Psychic Blast.

special_powers.name: MIND HUNTER
special_powers.description: Despero may modify either his attack or damage value by +1 when targeting an opposing character that can use Incapacitate, Mind Control, Outwit, or Penetrating/Psychic Blast.

special_powers.name: BLACKMARE CURSE
special_powers.description: When Blight is dealt penetrating damage, it can be reduced. Once per turn, an opposing character can be given a free action to be dealt 1 unaviodable damage and that character ignores this ability until your next turn.

special_powers.name: THIS EVIL DIDN'T CHOOSE ME, I CHOSE IT!
special_powers.description: Once per turn when a KO click on this dial is revealed, instead of being KO'd, heal Blight of damage equal to any further damage remaining to be taken. If there is no further damage, KO this character. This ability can't be ignored.

special_powers.name: YOUR DEATH BRINGS ME POWER
special_powers.description: When Mazahs! KO's an opposing character, choose a standard power that character possessed on any click. Mazahs! can use that power for the rest of the game.

special_powers.name: THE DARK LIGHTNING
special_powers.description: Mazahs! can use Pulse Wave. When he does, after actions resolve, each opposing character hit by the attack must choose a power it possesses. All other powers on these characters are countered until your next turn.

special_powers.name: SINFUL INFLUENCE
special_powers.description: When you build your force, you may assign the JLTW #S101 Envy relic to a friendly character without the Seven Deadly Sins keyword by paying its cost. This object doesn't count towards your force.

special_powers.name: LOOK INTO THE MIRROR
special_powers.description: Envy can't be targeted by ranged combat attacks.

special_powers.name: FEED FROM YOUR ENVY
special_powers.description: Envy can use Perplex. When Envy uses it to target another character, modify the same combat value on Envy by +1 until your next turn.

special_powers.name: SINFUL INFLUENCE
special_powers.description: When you build your force, you may assign the JLTW #S102 Sloth relic to a friendly character without the Seven Deadly Sins keyword by paying its cost. This object doesn't count towards your force.

special_powers.name: FREED FROM YOUR SLOTH
special_powers.description: After an action given to an opposing character within 4 squares resolves, the character given the action can't be given further actions this turn.

special_powers.name: YOU LEARN A LOT RESTING
special_powers.description: Opposing characters within 2 squares possess Earthbound/Neutralized. Sloth's damage value can't be modified.

special_powers.name: SINFUL INFLUENCE
special_powers.description: When you build your force, you may assign the JLTW #S103 Pride relic to a friendly character without the Seven Deadly Sins keyword by paying its cost. This object doesn't count towards your force.

special_powers.name: FEED FROM YOUR PRIDE
special_powers.description: When an opposing character rolls a critical hit, put a Pride token on this card. Give Pride a free action and remove a Pride token and her next attack is a critical hit and can't be rerolled.

special_powers.name: FOLLOW ME!
special_powers.description: Pride can use Defend, Leadership, Toughness, and the Colossal Stamina ability.

special_powers.name: SINFUL INFLUENCE
special_powers.description: When you build your force, you may assign the JLTW #S104 Greed relic to a friendly character without the Seven Deadly Sins keyword by paying its cost. This object doesn't count towards your force.

special_powers.name: MORE THAN ONE NEEDS
special_powers.description: When you build your force, you may assign a relic of 8 points or less to Greed by paying its cost. This object doesn't count towards your force.

special_powers.name: FEED FROM YOUR GREED
special_powers.description: Greed can use Mind Control. When he does, if the hit character ends that action adjacent to Greed, give the hit character up to 2 action tokens.

special_powers.name: ALL MINE
special_powers.description: Greed can use Perplex, but only to modify his own combat values.

special_powers.name: SINFUL INFLUENCE
special_powers.description: When you build your force, you may assign the JLTW #S105 Lust relic to a friendly character without the Seven Deadly Sins keyword by paying its cost. This object doesn't count towards your force.

special_powers.name: FEED FROM YOUR LUST
special_powers.description: Opposing characters can't make ranged combat attacks if they are adjacent to another character. This ability can't be ignored.

special_powers.name: GRASPING TENDRILS
special_powers.description: Lust can use Charge and Plasticity. Adjacent opposing characters modify their combat values by -1. If they have 2 action tokens, they modify them by an additional -1.

special_powers.name: SINFUL INFLUENCE
special_powers.description: When you build your force, you may assign the JLTW #S106 Wrath relic to a friendly character without the Seven Deadly Sins keyword by paying its cost. This object doesn't count towards your force.

special_powers.name: SPREADING WRATH
special_powers.description: When an opposing character makes an attack, after actions resolve give them a Wrath token. Character with Wrath tokens possess Battle Fury. When a character with a Wrath token clears action tokens, remove all Wrath tokens from it.

special_powers.name: LET ME AT THEM!
special_powers.description: Wrath can use Charge. When Wrath has one or more action tokens he can use the Giant Reach ability. When he has two action tokens, he can use Sidestep.

special_powers.name: FREED FROM YOUR WRATH
special_powers.description: Wrath can use Battle Fury. Modify his damage value by +1 for each other character within 5 squares that can use Battle Fury.

special_powers.name: SINFUL INFLUENCE
special_powers.description: When you build your force, you may assign the JLTW #S107 Gluttony relic to a friendly character without the Seven Deadly Sins keyword by paying its cost.  This object doesn't count towards your force.

special_powers.name: FEED FROM YOUR GLUTTONY
special_powers.description: Gluttony can use Steal Energy.  Opposing characters within 5 squares can't be healed.

special_powers.name: MOUNTAINS OF FLAB
special_powers.description: Gluttony can't be carried.  When Gluttony is dealt damage, Gluttony ignores all but 1 damage.  This power can't be countered or ignored.

special_powers.name: AURA OF ROT AND DECAY
special_powers.description: Gluttony can use Exploit Weakness.  When Gluttony hits an opposing character, remove any relic and resource attachments assigned to it from the game.  Relics and resource attachments can't be assigned to that character this game.

special_powers.name: BIO FISSION
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, place JLTW Jaina Hudson adjacent to White Rabbit in your starting area. If White Rabbit would be KO'd while this Jaina Hudson is on the map, instead place White Rabbit in your starting area on click #3 and your opponent scores 35 victory points.

special_powers.name: CATCH ME IF YOU CAN
special_powers.description: White Rabbit can use Leap/Climb and Sidestep. Give White Rabbit a double power action and place her in any square on the map that is not within line of fire of any opposing character.

special_powers.name: IN CONTACT WITH MY OTHER SELF
special_powers.description: Give Jaina Hudson a power action and heal an adjacent character named White Rabbit 2 clicks.

special_powers.name: E.M.P.
special_powers.description: When Roy Harper hits a character and actions resolve, choose one hit character. Roy Harper can use Outwit targeting that character.

special_powers.name: RULER OF ATLANTIS
special_powers.description: If an opponent wins the roll to determine the first player and doesn't choose a map with at least 12 printed squares of water terrain, characters on that opponent's force modify their speed values by -1.

special_powers.name: FROM THE DEPTHS
special_powers.description: When Aquaman is part of an Atlantis themed team, you may give Aquaman a free action and place 2 water terrain markers, one in his own square and the other in an adjacent square. Remove both markers at the beginning of your next turn.

special_powers.name: ATLANTIS RISES
special_powers.description: Aquaman can use Empower and Leadership.

special_powers.name: SAFETY FROM THE LAND DWELLERS
special_powers.description: Mera can use Energy Shield/Deflection. When Mera is part of an Atlantis themed team and occupies water terrain, she can use Barrier as a free action, but only to place 2 squares of blocking terrain.

special_powers.name: TIDAL WAVE
special_powers.description: Atlantean can use Charge. When Atlantean is part of an Atlantis themed team and hits with a close combat attack, you may choose that it generates knock back if it doesn't already. This knock back can't be ignored.

special_powers.name: SCHOOLING
special_powers.description: The Trench can use Sidestep. The Trench can use the Carry ability, but only to carry characters with both the Atlantis and Monster keywords.

special_powers.name: MOVE & CONTAIN
special_powers.description: D.E.O. Agent can use Plasticity and Sidestep.

special_powers.name: METAHUMAN POWER DAMPENING
special_powers.description: Adjacent opposing characters can't have their combat values increased. If D.E.O. Agent is part of a D.E.O. themed team, adjacent opposing characters can't use team abilities.

special_powers.name: APOKOLIPS RISING
special_powers.description: When Parademon uses the Carry ability, it may ignore the speed symbol of characters with the Apokolips keyword.

special_powers.name: SHAPE SHIFTERS & CON ARTISTS
special_powers.description: If Black Orchid is part of a Justice League Dark theme team, the first time each game that a friendly character not named Black Orchid would be dealt damage by an attack, you may instead chose to deal that damage to Black Orchid. If you do, place Black Orchid and the friendly character in each other's squares.

special_powers.name: AN ARROW FOR EVERY SITUATION
special_powers.description: Green Arrow starts the game with 6 Arrow tokens on this card. Give Green Arrow a free action to remove one token from this card and he may choose one of these powers or abilities to use until his next turn: Energy Explosion, Incapacitate, Penetrating/Psychic Blast, Smoke Cloud, Improved Targeting: Elevated, or Improved Targeting: Destroy Blocking.

special_powers.name: TAKE THE SHOT AND FADE AWAY
special_powers.description: Green Arrow can use Running Shot and Stealth. When he uses Running Shot and actions resolve, he can use Sidestep.

special_powers.name: ONE THING INTO ANOTHER
special_powers.description: Give Firestorm a free action and choose an unoccupied square of clear, hindering, or water terrain within line of fire. Place a blocking terrain marker in that square until you use this ability again.

special_powers.name: TOO MANY VARIABLES
special_powers.description: Once per turn, Firestorm can use either Outwit or Perplex.

special_powers.name: DOING WHAT NEEDS TO BE DONE
special_powers.description: Give Lex Luthor a power action and KO an adjacent friendly character of at least 50 points. When he does and as long as Lex Luthor is on the map, friendly characters can use Willpower.

special_powers.name: THIS IS A JOB FOR LEX LUTHOR
special_powers.description: Lex Luthor can use Mastermind. He may use it to transfer damage to a friendly character named "Bizarro" within 3 squares regardless of point cost.
This character can use Energy Shield/Deflection and Sidestep.  When making an attack, you may replace this character's attack value with one of its target's attack values.
This character can use Sidestep and modifies its defense value by +1. At the end of your turn, if this character wasn't given any actions this turn, heal it of 1 damage.
This character can use Energy Shield/Deflection and Sidestep.  This character's attack rolls of 11 are also critical hits.
This character can use Energy Shield/Deflection and Sidestep.  This character can use Perplex with a range value of 10, but only to target opposing characters assigned a relic or resource.
This character can use Combat Reflexes, Plasticity, and Sidestep.
This character can use Combat Reflexes, Sidestep, and Willpower.  Adjacent opposing characters can't use Shape Change.
This character can use Combat Reflexes and Sidestep. Give this character a free action to destroy an adjacent wall or square of blocking terrain.

special_powers.name: Ocean Depths
special_powers.description: Characters ignore the water terrain for movement purposes. Characters that can use the Swim ability modify their speed value y +2 and can use Improved Movement: Hindering, Elevated, Characters. Objects may be placed as though water terrain is clear terrain.
